# Performance Test Scripts

This directory contains performance test scripts (k6/JMeter).

## Running Performance Tests

```bash
# Using k6
k6 run scripts/load-test.js

# Using JMeter
jmeter -n -t scripts/test-plan.jmx -l reports/results.jtl
```

## Test Types

- Load testing
- Stress testing
- Endurance testing
- Spike testing
